00:12:51.471 --> 00:12:52.105
&gt;&gt; The other one.

00:12:52.105 --> 00:12:55.442
&gt;&gt; Yeah so.

00:12:55.442 --> 00:12:58.903
Sorry yes completing things
like list of three items.

00:13:00.990 --> 00:13:02.730
&gt;&gt; Yeah, I&#39;m only gonna say
I just don&#39;t think

00:13:02.730 --> 00:13:06.410
there&#39;s any wrong place to
find people, so when I

00:13:06.410 --> 00:13:09.080
look back at our first few
folks that we hired.

00:13:09.080 --> 00:13:10.090
They came from all over the
place.

00:13:10.090 --> 00:13:12.159
Like I put up ads on
Craigslist.

00:13:12.159 --> 00:13:14.162
I went to random tech talks.

00:13:14.162 --> 00:13:15.642
You know, we met people at,

00:13:15.642 --> 00:13:18.190
we used to throw weekly
barbeques at the office.

