00:13:42.394 --> 00:13:45.000
Triple so, when no one&#39;s
ever heard of or

00:13:45.000 --> 00:13:47.301
is using the product that
you&#39;re working on.

00:13:47.301 --> 00:13:52.110
&gt;&gt; Yeah it&#39;s probably really
important to

00:13:52.110 --> 00:13:55.140
have a great elevator pitch.

00:13:55.140 --> 00:13:56.847
Not even for investors, but

00:13:56.847 --> 00:13:59.979
just because everyone you
run into right now is maybe

00:13:59.979 --> 00:14:03.730
six months, a year down the
road, a potential recruit.

00:14:03.730 --> 00:14:06.280
And so, the right time to
have gotten them

00:14:06.280 --> 00:14:08.200
excited about your company,
the right time for

00:14:08.200 --> 00:14:09.620
them to have started
following us,

00:14:09.620 --> 00:14:11.820
and be thinking about it if
